
Out of the Abyss Bond 1		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 01	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:1. You were once lost in the Underdark, and a group of kuo-toa helped you fuid your way out Vou learned that there are kindly Folk even among that otherwise mad race, and remain indebted to them For their aid.
Out of the Abyss Bond 2		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 02	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:2. You once had the opportunity to meet a circle of myconids --the mushroom folk of the Underdark. They offered you shelter and a chance to "meld" using their telepathtc spores, and you have yearned ever since to repeat that experience.
Out of the Abyss Bond 3		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 03	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:3. One of your best friends in your youth was Morista Malkin, a shield dwarf and member of the Emerald Enclave. Though you haven't seen her in years, you heard she found her way to the reclaimed dwarfhold Gauntlgrym.
Out of the Abyss Bond 4		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 04	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:4. You once worked for Davra lassur, a Zhentarim "troubleshooter" recruiting promising new talent for the black Network. She helped you get your start as an adventurer, and you owe her for that.
Out of the Abyss Bond 5		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 05	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:5. You have long had a curious recurring dream about Visiting a vaulted stone library in the depths or the Underdark, and becoming lost in the endless lore it holds.
Out of the Abyss Bond 6		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 06	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:6. You studied with a deep gnome alchemist and miner named Kazook Pickshhine, who saved your life once when a magical experiment went awry. Last you heard, his family controlled some ofthe largest mines in the deep gnome settlement of Blingdenstone.
Out of the Abyss Bond 7		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 07	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:7. What little you lmow about the Underdark you learned from living and fighting alongside the Feldrun clan of dwarves. You swore an honor debt to the clan before they joined the forces retaking Gauntlgrim and established themselves there.
Out of the Abyss Bond 8		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 08	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:8. Years ago, a vicious noble named Chazrim DuLoc was implicated in the death of someone you cared about. The crime was covered up, though, and DuLoc disappeared. Rumor has it the zhentarim aided his escape, but you've sworn to find him one day.
Out of the Abyss Bond 9		CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 09	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:9. Years ago, you lost people you loved in a raid by creatures from the underdark They disappeared without a trace, either slain or taken into the depths. and you've always wondered whether they might still be alive and held as prisoners
Out of the Abyss Bond 10	CATEGORY:Special Ability	KEY:OotA ~ Bond 10	TYPE:Bond.Out of the Abyss Bond	COST:0	DESC:10. You know the dwarfhold Gauntlgrym well, having fought alongside the dwarves to help reclaim it. King Bruenor Battlehammer congratulated you on your valor, and you know the price the dwarves paid in blood to regain their home.


Optional Feature: Deep Delver			KEY:OotA ~ Deep Delver	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Optional Feature.Background Feature	COST:0	FACT:ReplacesBackgroundFeature|True	DESC:You have a knack for making your way in the deep places of the world. You can recall the twists and turns of passageway and tunnels such that you can always retrace your steps underground. You're also well acquainted with foraging and survival in the Underdark, and can determine when sources of food and water are safe to consume. You can always find sufficient food and water for yourself and up to five other people in the Underdark, as long as sustenance is available in the area.
Optional Feature: Underdark Experience	KEY:OotA ~ Underdark Experience	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Optional Feature.Background Feature	COST:0	FACT:ReplacesBackgroundFeature|True	DESC:You are no casual visitor to the Underdark, but instead have spent considerable time there learning its ways. You are familiar with the various races, civilizations, and settlements of the Underdark, as well as its major routes for travel. If you fail an Intelligence check to recall some piece of Underdark lore, you know a source you can consult for the answer unless the DM rules that the lore is unknown.
